      "date": "2013-08-20 05:29:41.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 4: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/665d5242-0919-11e3-b004-52540035b04c).  Ran 14 tests.  No failures.",
