      "date": "2014-03-17 20:47:20.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 5:\n\n(1 comment)\n\nI rebased this to the latest master, since it was way back on 2.4.91.  I want to see if this is still hitting failures on current master, since several of the failures I saw were old bugs that had since been fixed.\n\nThe one minor issue reported here should still be fixed, as well as adding some tests to this code.\n\nIn particular, the conf-sanity.sh test_78 resize test should be changed to do an online resize to verify the ioctl is working.  Also, it would be good to add a sanity.sh test_52c() that tested e.g. \"chattr +T\" and lsattr on the root inode to verify this flag is set and then cleared with \"chattr -T\".",
