        "subject": "LU-137 mount: Ioctl passthrough mechanism for OST/MDT mntpts",
        "message": "LU-137 mount: Ioctl passthrough mechanism for OST/MDT mntpts\n\nThis patch implements an interface for sending IO Control (ioctl)\ncommands from userspace through the Lustre mount point to the\nunderlying ldiskfs filesystem to allow execution of filesystem-wide\nioctl() commands, such as resize.\n\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Dilger <andreas.dilger@intel.com>\nSigned-off-by: Swapnil Pimpale <spimpale@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: I9f7ac8b12747fcd630572b4f2a1db79fdef42d8e\n"
      },
